             was indicted for <rs id="t17850914-165-off764" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850914-165-off764" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850914-165-off764" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               that he, on the <rs id="t17850914-165-cd765" type="crimeDate">20th day of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-165-off764 t17850914-165-cd765"></join> last, feloniously and falsly did make, forge, and counterfeit, and cause and procure to be falsly made, forged, and counterfeited, and willingly aid, and assist in the false making, forging, and counterfeiting a certain order for payment of money, dated 18th April, 1785, with the name J. Wood thereto subscribed, purporting to be signed by 
