            </rs> and which said false, forged, and counterfeited order for the payment of money, was in the words and figures following, that is to say,</p>
               <p>"Messers. Hankey and Co. pay Mr. Barnes or bearer 17 l. 12 s. 6 d. J. Wood, April, 13th 1785." with intention to defraud the said 
               
